snippet.textDisplay:
Oh Bhai BRILLIANT BRILLIANT BRILLIANT 👏  

XULFI you're a visionary  !  From Seasoned singers to finding Raw talent  , to creative Set , costumes to Choreography.. all the dancers.  Performers.... MIND BLOWING !! 

And the fact that you are establishing livelihood to talented people from streets ... Yeh sabse Bara Kamal hai Dost !  

Standing ovation for everyone here ! 

As a true Punjabi at my Core and a Lahori ... this made me so Happy. !!  

Not to mention the sense of immense Pride I feel when I am seeing the world react to our Coke Studio and this Song !!
